{"tid":1936222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國英國都停公開考試，得香港學生賤過屎","createTime":"2020-03-21T05:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T06:13:24.000Z","uid":256094,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9bea0f027a2245383a34ac1183cad2300c2176f5","tid":1936222,"uid":256094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:57:03.000Z","msg":"可能香港班小朋友覺得<br />\n已經溫書好辛苦想快啲考完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但今次講緊係整個香港年輕一代嘅生命<br />\n以及香港社區爆發嘅風險<br />\n<br />\n大家自己諗下一個考試場地裏面會裝到幾多個學生<br />\n只要其中一間房賴嘢<br />\n考完試之後大家各散東西返去自己住嘅地方又繼續播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我當你哋嘅成績好到識飛<br />\n死咗之後都只係一條死屍<br />\n死唔去就仲慘肺功能永久受損你以後嘅人生就係咁先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但竟然去到而家都冇人出聲制止<br />\n又或者係要求延遲考試<br />\n<br />\n大家團結啲保護自己嘅年輕新一代好唔好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f65a6e0c7cdbd7da18e519a2f26fa7ac5cdab4","tid":1936222,"uid":256094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7d182ab1b50a7d08edf0d28c2f444da4e4d4c3","tid":1936222,"uid":256094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"大家之所以抗爭都係為咗有將來<br />\n<br />\n屌班小朋友就係我哋將來嘅一部份啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef209